{
 "file": "_STGX5B.bin",
 "source_size": 47652,
 "built_size": 50294,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1641",
   "jp_len": 100,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "あいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。つネハバパ·々ビブベミメちっぞャー（ルでロ尉ど{00}·{00}！か、Mさのな、{00}{01}！@{00}M避ぬな、{00}{01}ぁ可恶、这帮家伙算什么！刚打倒就又涌上{00}来！！",
   "zh_hex": "15161718191a1b6566676869016a026b6c6d032e6f70717204077375777a7c2c2d297e080a8230848632000400061b0213f0313302000106de001398303302000115e7c4e7de02e7b9e910e7dfe7fde889e7dde7bdef97e8bce7f5e848e7c5e8f1ed82ef4c00efcfef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16d7",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别松懈！总之、绝不能让任何人靠近设施{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e9e0ec6fef97e881e7cd02e91ce7b5e7c6e7f9e89aefbcefb2e8c7efd8eb43eb8d0009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1716",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哇啊啊啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea88e7c3e7c3e7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x175c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、喂！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e8bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17ba",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！就没点办法吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e7c5e7d8e822e8eae84ee802ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17e6",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可您就算这么说、这里的守备队也就{00}那么点人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e835e7c5e889e7b9e7bde7ed02e7b9ef31e7b4e8a8e877e7c9e7c0e7c500e7b7e7bde822efb2090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x181d",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是还有那个实验体、还有原型机吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b6e7f7e7cbe7b7e828e87fea99bc02e7f7e7cbe8e4e977e7e4e8020605000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1833",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "都什么时候了、还舍不得拿出来用！",
   "zh_hex": "15e840e7dde7bdef2dea39e7ba02e7f7eb17e7b5e80ae9a7efbeefcfefb3ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x185d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1866",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1889",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂！你傻站着发什么呆！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bdef97e7b8ec0aec31e86de870e7dde7bdedf4ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18bc",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18ea",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、不好！快来人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7b5e7c7ef97e85fefcfefb20909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "给我站住！",
   "zh_hex": "15e839efccec31e859ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x195f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你这家伙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c5",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "咦……不是嘛",
   "zh_hex": "15ef490909e7b5e7b6e936000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19f8",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bd05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a1e",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还『什么』呢、大叔！蒂法在哪儿！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f70ce7dde7bd0de90702efa5ed2eef97e9f5e84eef29e8ffeb7cef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a55",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蒂法？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f5e84e05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a79",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是你们抓走的那个女孩！她就在这里吧{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6e7b8e7bbe962e890e7b4e7b7e828efade956ef97e88ee7c5ef29e7b9ef31e7d000ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab0",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "女孩？难不成、是前阵子弄来的那个实验{00}体……",
   "zh_hex": "15efade95605e866e7b5e83702e7b6ef51eb48e886eac4efcfe7b4e7b7e828e87fea9900ef4f09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aee",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……加洛德？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e854e94ae82c050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b0d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "加洛德！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e854e94ae82c060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b32",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蒂法！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f5e84eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b5e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蒂法！我来救你了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f5e84eef97efccefcfe8cae7b8e7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b8d",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "加洛德……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e854e94ae82c090906000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bba",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊！实验体她……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3ef97e87fea99ef4fe88e0909ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1be6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这家伙！到底是什么人！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97e7d7e9b4e7b6e7dde7bdefb2ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c1a",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说什么呢！抓走蒂法的明明是你们！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7dde7bde907ef97e962e890e9f5e84ee7b4ef39ef39e7b6e7b8e7bbef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c33",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蒂法我要带走了！不许你们有半句怨言！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f5e84eefccef2ae937e890e7baef97e7b5e8a7e7b8e7bbe7cbeadeebb9ec19efd7ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c75",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蠢货！你以为能从这里逃得出去吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e94beaf5ef97e7b8e7f3e7c1e7c6e88ae7b9ef31e8c2e80aefbee7ebe802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cab",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种事、不试试看怎么会知道！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1a902e7b5e91de91de7f6e7f2e7bde7e2e85ae82a06000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ce6",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！走！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97e890ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cf2",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "会有点摇晃、你忍着点、蒂法！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e2e7cbe822ebccec2002e7b8eb59e86de82202e9f5e84eef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d30",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！这帮家伙还真难缠！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e7b9e910e7dfe7fde7f7e820e866ec34ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d5e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……加洛德",
   "zh_hex": "150909e854e94ae82c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d8a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那里……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ef3109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1db2",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、机库？",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7e4e9b3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1de1",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……去那边",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ebe7b7e899000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e04",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到那边去就行了吧、蒂法？……好！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e7b7e899e7ebe7c5efd6e7bae7d002e9f5e84e050909e7c7ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e45",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "莫、莫非那个少年……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eba002eba0e8f0e7b7e828eface9090909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e6b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那个",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e828000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e94",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……MS！？这不是高达吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909efa7ef9eef9705e7b9e7b5e7b6e812ef2be802ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec4",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、好厉害……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e7c7ecbbe98809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ef4",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！！什、什么情况！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97ef97e7dd02e7dde7bde88be8d0ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f28",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好家伙、是头目啊……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7dfe7fd02e7b6e92eefd4e7c30909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f59",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙……要来！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fd0909ef2aefcfef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f6c",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正合我意！我立马反过来收拾你们！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3befc0efccef3cef97efcce86be84fe87cef36efcfe926eae6e7b8e7bbef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fba",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不行",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5efd6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fc1",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快逃……加洛德",
   "zh_hex": "15e85fe8c20909e854e94ae82c000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ff0",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蒂法？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f5e84e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2028",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那东西……已经开不了火了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8bae7f80909ef3ae8b7e7fae7b5e7bae8dae7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x205b",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……咦？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef4905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2094",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "力量、用得太多了……",
   "zh_hex": "15dae85102d8e80ae86ae7e9e7ba0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20c5",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么会……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7e20909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2100",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没事的、少年！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8efb8e7b402eface909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x213b",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "出来吧、高达啊啊啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efbeefcfe7d002e812ef2be7c3e7c3e7c3ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x217c",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b8e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21a1",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "有勇气的少年啊、你叫什么名字？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cbeadde8ede7b4eface909e7c302e7b8e8c1e7dde7bde8ace9800500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21ce",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶、啊……？啊、我、我叫加洛德",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf302e7c3090905e7c3028b028be8c1e854e94ae82c00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21fd",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "尽管放心、加洛德、那台恶魔高达是我的{00}敌人",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f2e93be86ce82d02e854e94ae82c02e7b7ea16e7dee8d8e812ef2be7b68be7b400e7e3b4000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2214",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "卡拉巴的人马上就会赶到、在那之前你能{00}撑住吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e801e7c2e85be7b4efb2e84fef4ce7c5e7e2ea04e7d702ef29e7b7e7cdef51e7b8e7c600ea29e859e802ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x224c",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦、哦……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91902e9190909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x227b",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、走！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e890ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22ab",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……这副惨状",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7b9ecb6ed5de98b0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22dd",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "东方不败·亚洲尊者！这也是你干的好事{00}吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bad0e7b5e88f04e7d6eacdeccdad06e7b9e7c0e7b6e7b8e8d3e7b4e7c7a900e802060500000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2311",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵……是多蒙啊",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3d0909e7b6e7e9e942e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x231a",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "老夫只不过是一路追着恶魔高达而来",
   "zh_hex": "15e9cae830ef32e7b5ef36e7b6efb6e8d2e8dde86de7dee8d8e812ef2be89cefcf00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x234b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真的吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b4e802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x236e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……真是个疑心重的家伙",
   "zh_hex": "150909e820e7b6e828eb62e82de8a1e7b4e7dfe7fd000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x237c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那也罢！现在就让你看看证据！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c0eaefef97e82fef29e7c5e7f9e7b8e7f6e7f6eba3e8ccef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ba",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下没什么怨言了吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4de7d8e7dde7bdec19efd7e7bae7d0ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23c9",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哈啊啊！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7e8e7c3e7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23f8",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上吧、多蒙！把那群死亡军团统统打飞！",
   "zh_hex": "15b2e7d002e7e9e94206e81be7b7ecfaa7ebb2e7e0ea5ee929e929e7f5ea4506000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2432",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、不用你说！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7b5efb3e7b8e7edef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2472",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那边的少年、也没问题吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e899e7b4eface90902e7c0e7d8e997ea12e7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24a1",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶？啊、嘛……你肯帮忙的话、我自然求{00}之不得",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf305e7c302e9360909e7b8e93de910ea06e7b4e81f02efccefb5e7efe93a00e7cde7b5e80a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24e8",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、出击！多蒙、加洛德！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02afe7cc06e7e9e94202e854e94ae82c06060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x251f",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、没完没了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02e7d8e87ee7d8e7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x256b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……你还记得吗、多蒙？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909e7b8e7f7e996e80ae80202e7e9e94205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x257d",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当年与你修行之时、我们被狼群袭击的那{00}回",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e909e832e7b8e9b0efd6e7cdef2d02efcce7bbe7f1ec7becfae9aee7cce7b4e7b700ef5200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25c1",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "师父……难道说？",
   "zh_hex": "15e96ce8880909e866e82ae7ed050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25fd",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没错！还有、当时也是如此！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e885ef97e7f7e7cb02ef53ef2de7c0e7b6e7f0e7caef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x260d",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我曾使出过流派东方不败的最终奥义！！",
   "zh_hex": "158bea2ae83fafef36ea2ee985e8bad0e7b5e88fe7b4e8c5e8e2e82be8ce0606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2658",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看好了、多蒙！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e7c7e7ba02e7e9e942ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x267f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、好厉害……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e7c7ecbbe98809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26af",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……多蒙！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7e9e942ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26d4",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多蒙·卡修、你没事吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e942ef4be801e9b002e7b8e7d8efb8e7d0ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x271d",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来你的伙伴们到了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7b8e7b4e7fdea72e7bbe7d7e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x272f",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一次、就把恶魔高达暂且交给你们了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6e86402e7c5e81be7dee8d8e812ef2be9ffe999e861e839e7b8e7bbe7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2748",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "告辞了、多蒙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e5ec9ae7ba02e7e9e942ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2778",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "站住、东方不败！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec31e85902e8baefb1e7b5e88fef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27b6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……还有什么事找老夫吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f7e7cbe7dde7bdefb8e9d2e9cae830e802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ea",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "告诉我、东方不败！你究竟为何盯上恶魔{00}高达！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e5ead6efcc02e8baefb1e7b5e88fef97e7b8e906ef2ce7c1efbceb95ef4ce7dee8d800e812ef2bef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2808",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是想利用恶魔高达、来毁灭地球吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e7e6e82ed8e7dee8d8e812ef2b02d9e97ce8e1bf95e802060500000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x285e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……迟早你会明白",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea10e963e7b8e7e2ef39e8090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x288c",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "东方不败！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8baefb1e7b5e88fef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28c7",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "石破天惊拳、我确实已经传给你了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef44ef6de844ec6dea6502efcce88ce87fef3ae8b7ea38e839e7b8e7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28db",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "告辞了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e5ec9ae7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2937",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "东方不败……你到底是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8baefb1e7b5e88f0909e7b8e7d7e9b4e7b6090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x296d",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、多蒙·卡修？刚才那位、似乎是{00}东方不败……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02e7e9e942ef4be801e9b005e8bce836e7b7e83402e944e933e7b600e8baefb1e7b5e88f09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29bd",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不、没什么大不了的事",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b502e7d8e7dde7bdefa5e7b5e7bae7b4efb80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29fa",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗、那么、我们现在就赶往你那边",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e80202e7b7e7bd02efcce7bbe82fef29e7c5ea04e911e7b8e7b7e89900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a0d",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在我们会合之前、你无论如何要撑住",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efcce7bbe7e2efc0e7cdef5102e7b8e7dce8dce7f0efbcef2aea29e8590000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a53",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白了！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e809e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a81",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "老夫竟会失手……失策！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9cae830ef2ce7e2e8a5ef660909e8a5ebe4ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2acb",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！连恶魔高达都没能打倒……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e86ee7dee8d8e812ef2be840e7d8e7c6e7f5e8480909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b0f",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦！是把它干掉了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e919ef97e7b6e81be978e8d3e9d3e7bae802ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b41",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……还没结束！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7f7e7d8e868e895ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b7b",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那是怎么回事！伤口居然愈合了吗！{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb8ef97e8f9eabdea4ce7efed5fefc0e7bae802ef97000500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bb9",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来果然没那么好对付啊、恶魔高达……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe871e7efe7d8e7b7e7bde7c7e7bee97ee7c302e7dee8d8e812ef2b0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bf5",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……搞定了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ec1ce867e7bae802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c21",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不、要说的话、它败得也太干脆了些{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b502ef2ae7ede7b4e81f02e978e88fe80ae7c0e86ae8d3edafe7bae8a400090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c60",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂喂！它又再生了不成！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bde8bdef97e978e8f1e80bef8de7bae7b5e837ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c74",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙真是怪物！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fde820e7b6ea07e99eef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cad",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恶魔高达！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dee8d8e812ef2bef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cd1",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "又让它给跑了吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f1e7f9e978e839eb6fe7bae80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d03",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我早就清楚、事情没那么简单……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce963e7c5e995ebd302efb8e88be7d8e7b7e7bde9abe91809090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d1a",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但是、恶魔高达、迟早我会把你……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe7b602e7dee8d8e812ef2b02ea10e963efcce7e2e81be7b80909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d53",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8280909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d5b",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说、你是为了救蒂法·亚迪尔才战斗{00}的吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7ed02e7b8e7b6e7c1e7bae8cae9f5e84e04e7d6ea11e7e1e836ef28e7ff00e7b4e7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d92",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、毕竟我可是蒂法的骑士",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602ea2cef2cefcce7c4e7b6e9f5e84ee7b4eca3ef6400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2da2",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "提坦斯那帮家伙、竟想拿蒂法去做实验！",
   "zh_hex": "15e821e843e7c8e7b7e910e7dfe7fd02ef2ce7e6e9a7e9f5e84ee7ebe81ce87fea99ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dbd",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这种事、可绝对饶不了吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d1efb802e7c4e91ce7beeab5e7b5e7bae7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2de8",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蒂法她、作为新人类似乎拥有相当高的能{00}力",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f5e84ee88e02ef2fe7c1ef8aefb2e841e944e933eb35e7cbe8b1ef53e812e7b4e7c600efb0000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e08",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光是这样待在近处、就能感受到她的力量",
   "zh_hex": "15e83de7b6e7b9e7daeaa8ef2996e90302e7c5e7c6e87de8c8e7d7e88ee7b4dae8510000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e60",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、喂",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e8bd0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e68",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们该不会、也打算拿蒂法去做什么古怪{00}实验吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe898e7b5e7e202e7c0e7f5e889e9a7e9f5e84ee7ebe81ce7dde7bde84dea0700e87fea99e7d0ef970500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ea3",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "并非如此、我反倒认为应该保护她才对",
   "zh_hex": "15e957e8f0e7f0e7ca02efcce87ce848e8a0e7c1e873e898ea47e8e0e88ee836e7be00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2eda",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啥？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eabe050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2efd",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蒂法她拥有很高的新人类能力",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f5e84ee88eeb35e7cbe981e812e7b4ef8aefb2e841e7c6efb0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f14",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后、她很可能被企图恶用这份力量的人{00}盯上",
   "zh_hex": "15a2e7fe02e88ee981e7c4e7c6e7f1ebdaeb2de7ded8e7b9ea22dae851e7b4b400eb95b2000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f51",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然如此、那就不能放着她不管了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7f0e7ca02e7b7e7c5e7b5e7c6e86ce86de88ee7b5e93be7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2faa",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fcc",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽不敢说万无一失、但卡拉巴应该能护住{00}蒂法",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7b5e8cde7ede9f8e7dcefb6e8a502e7dbe801e7c2e85be873e898e7c6e8e0e85900e9f5e84e00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3008",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嘛、单凭一个人有极限、这点刚才我{00}也领教了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e93602e918ea49efb6e828efb2e7cbeacaeb2302e7b9e822e8bce836efcc00e7c0ea20eaace7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3026",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要蒂法说行、那就承蒙你们关照了",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae9f5e84ee7edefd602e7b7e7c5ea75e942e7b8e7bbe8bbea1ae7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x305f",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没事的、加洛德",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8a9e7b402e854e94ae82c0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x306e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这些人、和研究所那些人不一样……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e8a4efb202e7d3ea0ce906e7fbe7b7e8a4efb2e7b5efb6e7da09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30a0",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗、既然蒂法说行、那我也就没意{00}见了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e80202e8c4e7efe9f5e84ee7edefd602e7b7efcce7c0e7c5e7d8ef3c00e85ce7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30be",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就、多关照！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c502e7e9e8bbea1aef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30e9",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、欢迎你们、加洛德、还有蒂法",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302ea92e931e7b8e7bb02e854e94ae82c02e7f7e7cbe9f5e84e000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3113",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "加洛德……你也要去战斗吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e854e94ae82c0909e7b8e7c0ef2ae7ebef28e7ffe802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3142",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛……总不能白白受人照顾、那可不行",
   "zh_hex": "15e9360909e881e7b5e7c6e809e809e8c8efb2ea1aea1f02e7b7e7c4e7b5efd6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3157",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至少打算帮上一点忙",
   "zh_hex": "15e897eface7f5e889e910ef4cefb6e822ea06000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x318b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也要战斗、加洛德",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7c0ef2aef28e7ff02e854e94ae82c0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31b2",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶、蒂法？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf302e9f5e84e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31d5",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为我不能只让加洛德一个人去战斗……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c18be7b5e7c6ef32e7f9e854e94ae82c87e828b4e7ebef28e7ff09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3203",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可蒂法……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e9f5e84e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3229",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我没事的、因为有加洛德在我身边",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7d8a9e7b402ef33e7c1e7cbe854e94ae82cef298be88de89900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x326c",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……谢谢你、蒂法",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e8b2e8b2e7b802e9f5e84e000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9336",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么会败在这里……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7e2e88fef29e7b9ef3109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x950a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "马上就要抵达奥布了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84fef4ce7c5ef2ae96eef2be82be831e7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9534",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、向奥布政府申请着陆许可！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702efc1e82be831ea68ea60ec7ce83ae86defdae8a7e7c4ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9566",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们！平安无事就好！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbef97e887e7fce7dcefb8e7c5e7c7ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9592",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "卡嘉莉小姐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e801e89ee81ee83ee921ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x95b5",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您就是卡嘉莉·尤拉·阿斯哈吧、我们把{00}大天使号带来了",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7c5e7b6e801e89ee81eef4bea5fe7c2ef4be7d2e7c8e7e8e7d002efcce7bbe81b00efa5e844e83fe833e937efcfe7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x95ea",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要谢谢卡拉巴的各位、多亏你们平安把{00}他们带来",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae8b2e8b2e801e7c2e85be7b4e819e83402e7e9eab7e7b8e7bbe887e7fce81b00e80ce7bbe937efcf00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9623",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个……卡嘉莉小姐、关于基拉、他的事{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8280909e801e89ee81ee83ee92102e8bbe879e829e7c202e80ce7b4efb800090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x965d",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙一定还平安活着……我是这么相信{00}的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fdefb6e867e7f7e887e7fce8d4e86d0909efcce7b6e7b9e7bde8b1e90f00e7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9692",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "都怪我太没用……",
   "zh_hex": "15e840ea07efcce86ae7d8efb309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x96be",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别提了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e821e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x96c7",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起这个、家父说想见各位、和大家谈谈",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b9e82802e7dfe888e7ede7e6e85ce819e83402e7d3bee7dfeaf4eaf40000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x96e8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……请随我来",
   "zh_hex": "150909e83ae9a1efccefcf00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x970a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是最后通告！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6e8c5e7feef59e8e5ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9719",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对于一味只顾自保、屡次拒绝协助请求的{00}奥布联合首长国",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee879efb6ed36ef32ea1fefb5ea4702ee13e864eb07e91ce8f6ea23e83ae93ae7b400e82be831ef2eefc0ef40ef34efc40000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9741",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们地球联邦军要求如下！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbef63efd3ef2eefaae7e0ef2ae93ae7f0ef4def97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9754",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "其一！奥布联合首长国立即投降！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cfefb6ef97e82be831ef2eefc0ef40ef34efc4e86be855e948e943ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9768",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "其二！现政府及奥布军解除武装！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cfea13ef97e82fea68ea60e9cfe82be831e7e0e89de974e8ece98fef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x977f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若这些条件不被接受、我们将认定奥布为{00}敌对国……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7b9e8a4e9d4e991e7b5e7f1efcee8c802efcce7bbe84ae8a0e867e82be831e7c100e7e3e7beefc4090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x979e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "并将对贵国诉诸武力、加以对抗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e957e84ae7bee930efc4ead6ea56e8ecefb002e854e7f3e7bee912ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9812",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这就是昨天、我们从联邦军收到的通信",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c5e7b6ece1e84402efcce7bbe88aef2eefaae7e0e926e7d7e7b4ef59e90f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9845",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么最后通告！？那分明就是露骨的胁迫{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bde8c5e7feef59e8e5ef9705e7b7efaeef39e7c5e7b6e858eb76e7b4edadeb7000ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x987a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这正是提坦斯的一贯做派、不肯顺从的就{00}用武力清除",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef3be7b6e821e843e7c8e7b4efb6ed07e81ce98502e7b5e93deab4e88ae7b4e7c500efb3e8ecefb0e995e9740000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x98b4",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那帮家伙、就是想得到奥布的力量",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e910e7dfe7fd02e7c5e7b6e7e6e80ae7d7e82be831e7b4dae85100000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x98e0",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原来如此……他们的目标、多半是摩根罗{00}特公司吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca0909e80ce7bbe7b4efd4e96f02e7e9eadee7b6ee35e9b8e7ec00e7cfe9a4eafee7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9911",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我国一旦投降、那份力量立刻就会被用来{00}对付他们的敌人……",
   "zh_hex": "158ba187ebcde948e94302e7b7ea22dae851e86be91fe7c5e7e2e7f1d8d900e7bee97ee80ce7bbe7b4e7e3b409090000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9938",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……比如扎夫特、比如宇宙殖民地、这有{00}违奥布的理念",
   "zh_hex": "150909e825e7f0e84be830e7cf02e825e7f0e8bee8bfe8a9ef38bf02e7b9e7cb00eab2e82be831e7b4e872ea27000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9976",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、乌兹米代表是打算拒绝这份通告了{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e94de856e878e8e7e9e7e7b6e7f5e889eb07e91ce7b9ea22ef59e8e5e7ba00050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x99ab",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、奥布的理念、是必须守护的",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502e82be831e7b4e872ea2702e7b6e860e9a2e8a8e8e0e7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x99c2",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正如各位所知、我国从不拒绝调整者",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7f0e819e834e7fbe85a02efccefc4e88ae7b5eb07e91ce95ce9feef6e00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x99d9",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "仅仅因为是调整者、因为是自然人、就这{00}样区别看待彼此……",
   "zh_hex": "15eb7aeb7aef33e7c1e7b6e95ce9feef6e02ef33e7c1e7b6efb5e7efefb202e7c5e7b900e7daef35e7e5e7f6eaa8efc9e7ca09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x99f2",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为我认为、正是这种思想、才会招致更{00}深的摩擦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c18be8a0e7c102ef3be7b6e7b9e7d1a6e7e602e836e7e2e97aea32e95200eb0de7b4ee35eb0a0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9a0e",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "将所有调整者一概视为恶、对这样的他们{00}、我绝不会附和",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ae7fbe7cbe95ce9feef6eefb6ec76e9d9e7c1e7de02e7bee7b9e7dae7b4e80ce7bb0002efcce91ce7b5e7e2eaf8e7d300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9a4c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们卡拉巴、愿尽全力支援奥布",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe801e7c2e85b02e961e8f2efb4efb0e883e863e82be8310000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9a8f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……多谢了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8650909e7e9e8b2e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ab5",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛琉·拉米亚斯、你们打算怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e845ead2ef4be7c2e878e7d6e7c802e7b8e7bbe7f5e889e7f2e7bde8ea05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ac9",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一来、就要和不久前还是友军的人交战{00}了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6efcf02e7c5ef2ae7d3e7b5e9dbef51e7f7e7b6e960e7e0e7b4efb2e861ef2800e7ba09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9b29",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……先让我问一个问题",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef8be7f9efcce997efb6e828e997ea120000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9b56",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……穆少佐？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eb10efacefba0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9b7b",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才乌兹米代表说的那番话、我也觉得确{00}实是个了不起的想法",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e94de856e878e8e7e9e7e7ede7b4e7b7ee6de81f02efcce7c0e8aee80ae88c00e87fe7b6e828e7bae7b5e847e7b4e7e6e84e0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9b9a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可那、不过是理想论罢了吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b702e7b5ef36e7b6e872e7e6e8dceaefe7bae7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9baf",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现实中、自然人和调整者、彼此都抱有{00}偏见",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fe87fc002abe7efb4e7d3e95ce9fead02c9e7cae840e922e7cb00eb4de85c00000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9bc9",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……地球和殖民地也一样、如今彼此都把{00}对方当敌人",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef63efd3e7d3e8a9ef38ef63e7c0efb6e7da02e7f0efb9efc9e7cae840e81b00e7beefb1ef53e7e3efb2000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9be8",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在这种局面下、守着理想、还有什么意义{00}吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9e7d1ea8ce862ef4d02e8a8e86de872e7e602e7f7e7cbe7dde7bdef3ce8ce00e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9c20",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我明白……当然、就连我国、也并非事事{00}都顺心",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef39e8090909ef53e7ef02e7c5e86eefccefc402e7c0e957e8f0efb8efb800e840eab4e82d000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9c44",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但若因此放弃、我们迟早只会落得彼此毁{00}灭的下场",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe7e7ef33e7cae86ce93802efcce7bbea10e963ef32e7e2e92ae80aefc9e7cae97c00e8e1e7b4ef4de8760000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9c82",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ca6",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "穆少佐……？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb10efacefba09090500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ccb",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、总之、事态已经紧迫到这种地步了",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e881e7cd02efb8e994ef3ae8b7eaedeb70e7d7e7b9e7d1ef63ea93e7ba0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ceb",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作为玛琉舰长、你应该没法坐视不管吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fe7c1e845ead2e7d4ef3402e7b8e873e898e7d8e84eecc3e9d9e7b5e93be7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9d56",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……乌兹米代表",
   "zh_hex": "150909e94de856e878e8e7e9e70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9d5f",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在向船员确认之前、我无法给出承诺、不{00}过……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efc1ea02e849e88ce8a0e7cdef5102efcce7dce84ee839efbeea75e97202e7b500ef360909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9d7b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请让我们朝着协助奥布的方向、考虑一下",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7f9efcce7bbeaade86de8f6ea23e82be831e7b4efb1efc102eb41eba1efb6ef4d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9dba",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9dfe",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你已经完全恢复精神了呢、基拉",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef3ae8b7e87ebbec69e9eee98de9aae7bae90702e829e7c20000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9e36",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉克丝……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e7d5e8a30909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9e62",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……基拉？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e829e7c2050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9e85",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉克丝……我要走了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e7d5e8a30909efccef2ae890e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ead",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您这是要去哪里呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b9e7b6ef2ae7ebe8ffef31e90705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9ed5",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……回地球、我、必须回去……",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef52ef63efd302efcc02e860e9a2ef52e7eb090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9f05",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为什么？就算您一个人回去、战斗也不会{00}结束的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dde7bd05e7c5e889e835efb6e828efb2ef52e7eb02ef28e7ffe7c0e7b5e7e200e868e895e7b40000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9f3f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9f46",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是……我已经没法再待在这里、只是干{00}看着了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b60909efccef3ae8b7e7d8e84ee80beaa8ef29e7b9ef3102ef32e7b6e8d300e7f6e86de7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9f60",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要回地球了、拉克丝",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2aef52ef63efd3e7ba02e7c2e7d5e8a3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9f8b",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9fce",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "结果退舰的才11人……一个个都挺有种{00}嘛、看来阿拉斯加是真把大家惹毛了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e868e871e880e7d4e7b4e836eff7eff7efb20909efb6e828e828e840eb5ce7cbe7d100e93602e7f6efcfe7d2e7c2e7c8e854e7b6e820e81befa5e7dfecd7eb60e7ba0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa010",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "少佐您……当时为什么回来了呢？在阿拉{00}斯加……",
   "zh_hex": "15efacefbae8350909ef53ef2de7c1e7dde7bdef52efcfe7bae90705ef29e7d2e7c200e7c8e8540909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa046",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf305000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa04d",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真拿你没办法……没想到事到如今你还会{00}问起这个",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e9a7e7b8e7d8e8eae84e0909e7d8e7e6e7d7efb8e7d7e7f0efb9e7b8e7f7e7e200e997e847e7b9e82800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa083",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……穆少佐？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eb10efacefba0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa0a8",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "理由嘛……",
   "zh_hex": "15e872e8a6e93609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa0b0",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……因为有你在、玛琉·拉米亚斯",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef33e7c1e7cbe7b8ef2902e845ead2ef4be7c2e878e7d6e7c800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa0dc",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa0fe",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……真不像我、竟动了真心",
   "zh_hex": "150909e820e7b5e8e9efcc02ef2cef30e7bae820e82d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa12d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "穆……",
   "zh_hex": "15eb1009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa19a",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa1a7",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一直玩到{00}了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e875e970e7d700e7bae8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa1c7",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗就在此暂告一{00}段落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ffe7c5ef29e7cae9ffe8e5efb600ea6be92a090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa1e6",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请你尽情{00}享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88b00ec06e8c80000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa20b",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为通关本路线的你、还准备了特别{00}关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7bae7cfe7e500e8bbe80100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa232",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与另行奋战至今的大天使队进行的特{00}别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832e99befd6ef46ef28e897efb9e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cf00e7e5ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa253",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}实力也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e87fefb0e7c0e7b5e8850000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa278",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便可与{00}他们一战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c4e83200e80ce7bbefb6ef280000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa29d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa2c1",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也请你尽情游玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88bea94e970e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa33a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一直陪着我这个不可靠的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef340000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa359",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa377",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽然我们预防者的战斗已经结束{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7ef8be7bbea5ae968ade7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa391",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……但游戏本身仍可继续、之后也请尽情{00}享受",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae8f2e88b00ec06e8c8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa3b7",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还为通关这条路线的你、准备了新的关卡{00}哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c1ef59e8bbe7b9e9d4e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e87ae877e7baef8ae7b4e8bbe80100e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa3db",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与曾和提坦斯、新吉翁交战的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832ea2ae7d3e821e843e7c802ef8ae7d9ee88e861ef28e7b40909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa3f6",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……隆德·贝尔队进行的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa409",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们交战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbe861ef2800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa42f",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必挑战",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860eae7ef28000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa43d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa461",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲过去吧、大天使号{00}！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95eef36e7ebe7d002efa5e844e83fe83300ef97ef970d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa4e2",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa4f2",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、要向你一路以来出色的指挥致以敬{00}意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802ef2a9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e949ea32e7f3ee3800ef3c00000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa514",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏有你的协助、我们才得以奋战到了最{00}后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7cbe7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3ef46ef28e7d7e7bae8c500e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa536",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa54c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽然我们主天使队的战斗已经结束{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7efefcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e89500090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa565",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请你尽情享{00}受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88bec0600e8c800000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa589",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续、此外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cae8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa5b4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa5d2",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、与他们一战你也必定能够取胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8b1e90f02e832e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7b8e7c0e860e867e7c6e920e987e8db000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa5f7",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa61b",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也祝你武运长久",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0ed97e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa6b6",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对、对不起……蒂法！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7be02e7bee7b5e8470909e9f5e84eef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa6fc",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "加洛德……你也要去战斗吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e854e94ae82c0909e7b8e7c0ef2ae7ebef28e7ffe802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa72b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛……总不能白白受人照顾、那可不行",
   "zh_hex": "15e9360909e881e7b5e7c6e809e809e8c8efb2ea1aea1f02e7b7e7c4e7b5efd6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa740",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至少打算帮上一点忙",
   "zh_hex": "15e897eface7f5e889e910ef4cefb6e822ea06000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa774",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也要战斗、加洛德",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7c0ef2aef28e7ff02e854e94ae82c0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa79b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶、蒂法？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf302e9f5e84e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa7be",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为我不能只让加洛德一个人去战斗……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c18be7b5e7c6ef32e7f9e854e94ae82c87e828b4e7ebef28e7ff09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa7ec",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可蒂法……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e9f5e84e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa812",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我没事的、因为有加洛德在我身边",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7d8a9e7b402ef33e7c1e7cbe854e94ae82cef298be88de89900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0xa855",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……谢谢你、蒂法",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e8b2e8b2e7b802e9f5e84e000000"
  }
 ]
}
